# Coverage Exclusions for aviate-core
# ====================================
# This file documents lines excluded from coverage requirements.
# Each exclusion must have a justification. The goal is 100% coverage
# of all non-excluded code to catch untested changes during development.
#
# Format: file:line  # REASON: justification
#
# Valid reasons:
#   STUB      - Placeholder implementation, not used in current configuration
#   DEFAULT   - Default trait impl for optional functionality
#   DEFENSIVE - Defensive code path that cannot be triggered in tests
#   EMPTY     - Empty match arm or block (no executable code)

# =============================================================================
# hal.rs - Hardware Abstraction Layer
# =============================================================================
hal.rs:29   # DEFAULT: read_airspeed() returns None for non-fixed-wing
hal.rs:30   # DEFAULT: (continuation)
hal.rs:31   # DEFAULT: (continuation)

